WEBVTT

00:00.233 --> 00:03.502
Owen: Previously
on "childrens hospital"...

00:03.504 --> 00:05.671
We're gonna have to evacuate
the hospital for 14 weeks.

00:05.673 --> 00:08.073
However, I got us all a job
as a private contractor

00:08.074 --> 00:09.875
At an army base in japan.

00:09.877 --> 00:12.277
But we're ambassadors,
so no betting on the operations.

00:12.279 --> 00:14.847
Are you paying me to keep quiet
while you throw this surgery

00:14.849 --> 00:16.081
Because
you bet money on it?

00:16.082 --> 00:17.616
Uh-huh.

00:17.618 --> 00:20.085
Tripper: You doctors have been
a real asset to the base.

00:20.087 --> 00:22.121
You got the pediatric clinic
on its feet

00:22.123 --> 00:24.056
And provided a lot of laughs
along the way.

00:24.058 --> 00:25.624
It's what we do.

00:25.626 --> 00:28.761
Ha! It's zingers like that
that I'm gonna miss the most.

00:28.763 --> 00:32.064
But now you all have to go back
to childrens hospital.

00:32.066 --> 00:34.299
Owen: It's gonna be nice
to get back to brazil...
Cat: Yeah.

00:34.301 --> 00:36.602
...Which, as we all know,
is where we were based

00:36.604 --> 00:38.537
Before we took this job
in japan...
Yeah.

00:38.539 --> 00:41.373
...Which is, as we also know,
where we've been.

00:41.375 --> 00:44.143
And where we are.
This is japan.
Yeah.

00:44.145 --> 00:45.978
Owen maestro,
you're under arrest!

00:45.980 --> 00:47.613
Hey, what's going on?!
[ grunts ]

00:47.615 --> 00:48.447
Owen!

00:52.685 --> 00:54.386
I love you, cat.

00:54.388 --> 00:55.254
I...

00:55.256 --> 00:56.688
You've been found guilty

00:56.690 --> 00:59.591
Of colluding with
a criminal surgery-fixing ring.

00:59.593 --> 01:00.793
I hereby sentence you

01:00.795 --> 01:03.062
To five years in
a maximum-security penitentiary.

01:03.064 --> 01:03.962
[ spectators gasping ]

01:03.964 --> 01:08.700
[ mid-tempo music plays ]

01:11.404 --> 01:14.139
By order of the elder council
of machines,

01:14.141 --> 01:16.341
All females of childbearing age

01:16.343 --> 01:19.445
Shall surrender to
a birthing farm for one year.

01:19.447 --> 01:23.782
What a bleak dystopian future
we've found ourselves in.

01:23.784 --> 01:26.985
[ chuckles ] thanks, guys.
Hit the lights!

01:26.987 --> 01:28.387
I could never have written

01:28.389 --> 01:31.190
My first speculative-fiction
novel without you guys.

01:31.192 --> 01:34.460
Hey, before you guys go, listen,
as you all know,

01:34.462 --> 01:36.728
My boyfriend, owen,
gets out of prison today,

01:36.730 --> 01:39.531
And, you know, he's been
locked up for five years,

01:39.533 --> 01:40.732
So make him feel at home.
[ chuckles ]

01:40.734 --> 01:42.668
Aw. Don't worry, cat.

01:42.670 --> 01:43.769
I have him scheduled

01:43.771 --> 01:47.072
For a very difficult
heart surgery today, so...

01:47.074 --> 01:48.373
That'll help.

01:48.375 --> 01:50.109
He hasn't performed surgery
in five years.

01:50.111 --> 01:51.376
I mean,
how's that gonna help?

01:51.378 --> 01:53.378
In ways I couldn't
possibly describe

01:53.380 --> 01:54.713
Without
incriminating myself.

01:54.715 --> 01:57.883
Hey, cat, uh,
you know what val and I do

01:57.885 --> 01:58.917
When we feel out of place?

01:58.919 --> 02:01.653
No.
We look at our award!

02:01.655 --> 02:04.389
Have you guys seen this thing?
Fastest team tonsillectomy.

02:04.391 --> 02:06.358
I mean, I don't know
what got into us that day.

02:06.360 --> 02:09.761
It's like
time just slowed down.

02:09.763 --> 02:12.064
I know a little something
about that.

02:12.066 --> 02:13.699
[ gasps ]
owen's back...

02:13.701 --> 02:16.235
...Pack!
Owen's backpack is back!

02:16.237 --> 02:18.670
[ laughing ]
look at this thing! Oh!

02:18.672 --> 02:22.241
Oh, yes!
I missed the backpack so much!

02:22.243 --> 02:24.143
Thanks for
not ratting me out.

02:24.145 --> 02:25.644
I'll make it up to you
somehow.

02:25.646 --> 02:27.880
[ scoffs ]
hey, where's my lady?

02:27.882 --> 02:31.783
Cat, I've been back in town
for almost a minute.

02:31.785 --> 02:34.786
Why aren't you riding this thing
in a supply closet right now?

02:34.788 --> 02:37.322
Because I'm pregnant.

02:37.324 --> 02:38.757
[ all gasp ]

02:38.759 --> 02:40.259
Oh, mazel tov!

02:41.194 --> 02:42.895
Look at those knockers!

02:43.863 --> 02:46.798
I've been standing behind
counters for seven months,

02:46.800 --> 02:49.401
Waiting for the perfect time
to tell you guys.

02:49.403 --> 02:52.738
Owen, aren't you gonna
say anything?

02:53.907 --> 02:55.741
I don't know
what to say.

02:55.743 --> 02:59.278
How about, "hello,"
to your unborn child, say?

02:59.280 --> 03:01.547
Cat, I haven't seen you
in five years.

03:01.549 --> 03:03.549
[ scoffs ]
what do you call

03:03.551 --> 03:05.884
The conjugal visit we had
seven months ago?

03:06.519 --> 03:14.126
That never happened,
so I call it...Fiction.

03:14.128 --> 03:17.029
Ah, my old office.

03:17.031 --> 03:20.365
Oh. Oh!

03:20.367 --> 03:21.800
What is that smell?

03:21.802 --> 03:23.368
There he is!

03:23.370 --> 03:25.137
Welcome back!
I'm so sorry.

03:25.139 --> 03:28.740
We had to re-zone your office
as a public fart room.

03:28.742 --> 03:31.543
But you've always got a place
here at childrens.

03:31.545 --> 03:33.478
Unless, of course,
your performance drops 4%,

03:33.480 --> 03:35.047
At which time,
you're out on your ass.

03:35.049 --> 03:37.382
Not me.
It's corporate policy.

03:37.384 --> 03:39.451
So have a good time,
read a magazine,

03:39.453 --> 03:41.887
Fart a little if you got one
in the chamber.

03:41.889 --> 03:44.756
What a pleasure
to see you back, huh?

03:44.758 --> 03:46.758
4%.

03:51.731 --> 03:52.831
[ knocks ]

03:52.833 --> 03:54.633
Penny for your thoughts, my lo--
[ coughs ]

03:54.635 --> 03:56.401
Who ripped a blast
in here?

03:56.403 --> 03:58.804
Smells like broken promises
to me, cat.

03:58.806 --> 04:02.107
Mm. No, it really smells
like a bathroom.

04:02.109 --> 04:05.210
How could you cheat on me
and claim that baby is mine?

04:05.212 --> 04:07.512
[ sighs ]
how could you not remember?

04:07.514 --> 04:10.682
We made love in a standalone
trailer like two wild animals.

04:10.684 --> 04:12.718
I'll never forget
what you said

04:12.720 --> 04:15.554
Right after your love exploded
inside of me --

04:15.556 --> 04:17.822
"that one
had a baby in it!"

04:17.825 --> 04:19.057
