04:20.793 --> 04:23.996
Are you okay to do that surgery?
It's in three hours.

04:23.998 --> 04:25.497
I don't know, cat.

04:25.499 --> 04:29.067
I just...Don't --

04:29.069 --> 04:30.235
Blake: Excuse me.

04:30.237 --> 04:32.704
[ fart ]

04:32.706 --> 04:34.906
Ahh!

04:34.908 --> 04:36.975
And excuse me again.
[ chuckles softly ]

04:36.977 --> 04:39.945
[ razor whirring ]

04:39.947 --> 04:42.881
[ click, whirring stops ]

04:42.883 --> 04:44.716
Listen, owen, I think

04:44.718 --> 04:47.519
I can finally make things
right between us.

04:48.187 --> 04:49.655
Check your hand.
[ chuckles ]

04:51.891 --> 04:54.159
Not interested!

04:54.161 --> 04:58.163
Well, get interested.
Your big surgery's in two hours.

04:58.165 --> 05:00.065
If you don't
take a dive -- unh!

05:01.167 --> 05:03.335
[ groans ]

05:03.337 --> 05:05.504
[ sighs ]
I can't handle this!

05:05.506 --> 05:08.774
Dr. Pippin: You sound just like
you did back in the joint...

05:08.776 --> 05:11.643
Cryin' over your lack of ability
to handle stuff.

05:11.645 --> 05:14.146
Dr. Ron pippin. What's
my old cellmate doing here?

05:14.148 --> 05:15.847
[ both chuckle ]

05:15.849 --> 05:17.316
Still can't believe
I shared a cell

05:17.318 --> 05:19.117
With the only other doctor
in lockup.

05:19.119 --> 05:20.352
What a coincidence.

05:20.354 --> 05:22.487
I don't believe
in coincidences.

05:22.489 --> 05:24.456
Then what are you
doing here, pippin,

05:24.458 --> 05:25.824
If it's
not a coincidence?

05:25.826 --> 05:28.260
Just a remarkable concurrence
of circumstances

05:28.262 --> 05:30.295
Without any
apparent connection.

05:30.297 --> 05:31.730
See you around, pal.

05:38.204 --> 05:40.472
Hey! There you are.
[ chuckles ]

05:40.474 --> 05:43.342
So glad you finally remember
our conjugal visit.

05:43.344 --> 05:45.310
I do?

05:45.312 --> 05:46.645
Yes.

05:46.647 --> 05:48.480
You said so an hour ago.

05:48.482 --> 05:49.715
You even
gave feedback on --

05:49.717 --> 05:51.483
On color choices
for the nursery.

05:51.485 --> 05:53.618
I think
I'm losing my mind.

05:57.857 --> 05:58.957
Oh.
Oh.

05:58.959 --> 06:01.626
Sorry. She's all yours.
Oh. [ scoffs ]

06:06.332 --> 06:07.666
[ sighs ]

06:11.304 --> 06:12.137
[ knock on door ]

06:12.139 --> 06:13.905
Knock, knock. Hey.

06:13.907 --> 06:14.539
Hey.

06:14.541 --> 06:15.474
How you doing, buddy?

06:15.476 --> 06:17.509
Not good, man.
Yeah.

06:17.511 --> 06:19.311
I work in a fart room.
Yeah.

06:19.313 --> 06:22.214
Okay? I don't remember putting
a baby inside of cat.
Yeah.

06:22.216 --> 06:24.182
Sy's gonna fire me
if I blow this surgery.
Yeah.

06:24.184 --> 06:27.185
But if I don't, chief's gonna
kill me with her finger.

06:27.187 --> 06:29.388
Yeah, yeah. Yeah.

06:29.390 --> 06:30.622
You know what I do
when I'm feeling blue?

06:30.624 --> 06:32.557
I like to look
at my award.

06:32.559 --> 06:33.925
[ chuckles ]
it's like time said --

06:33.927 --> 06:35.794
Yeah, I know.
Time said something.

06:35.796 --> 06:37.696
You guys took out
some tonsils really fast.

06:37.698 --> 06:39.531
It's --
it's inspiring, really.

06:39.533 --> 06:41.433
I'm glad you like it

06:41.435 --> 06:42.968
Because val and I would like
to give it to you.

06:42.970 --> 06:45.303
As inspiration.

06:45.305 --> 06:49.341
Okay. Okay, so...
Now I have this.

06:49.343 --> 06:51.777
You're welcome.
[ chuckles ]

06:53.946 --> 06:56.248
Excuse me. Sorry.

06:56.250 --> 06:57.682
Thought
I was done fartin',

06:57.684 --> 06:59.818
But apparently fartin'
isn't done with me.

06:59.820 --> 07:00.819
Come on, man.

07:00.821 --> 07:02.387
You're probably
gonna want to leave.

07:02.389 --> 07:03.622
It's gonna get pretty real
in here.

07:03.624 --> 07:05.023
Yeah, I don't need
to be here for this.

07:05.025 --> 07:08.059
Good luck
on the surgery!
Thank you.

07:08.061 --> 07:09.761
[ little fart ]

07:09.763 --> 07:13.131
Well, I guess
I kind of oversold that.

07:14.000 --> 07:16.935
You got this.
You got this.

07:16.937 --> 07:19.037
[ moaning ]

07:20.039 --> 07:21.473
[ gasps ] aah!

07:21.475 --> 07:23.642
Owen! That doctor
I've never seen before

07:23.644 --> 07:25.310
Is a dead ringer
for you.

07:25.312 --> 07:27.779
Cat,<i> I'm</i> owen.

07:27.781 --> 07:31.483
This is my former cellmate,
<i>ron pippin.</i>

07:31.485 --> 07:33.385
Looks like he's been
pretending to be me

07:33.387 --> 07:34.586
To have sex with you.

07:34.588 --> 07:36.288
How could you do this,
pippin?

07:36.290 --> 07:39.624
I just took advantage
of our uncanny resemblance.

07:39.626 --> 07:42.027
Good luck in there, owen.

07:42.029 --> 07:43.361
Chief.

07:43.363 --> 07:45.530
Aah! Ohh!

07:45.532 --> 07:48.300
Is madame tussaud here?

07:48.302 --> 07:50.469
[ chuckles ]
so real!

07:50.471 --> 07:51.736
Look at that!

07:51.738 --> 07:55.173
Chief,<i> I'm</i> owen.

07:56.142 --> 07:57.609
What did you want?

07:57.611 --> 08:00.912
[ grumbles ]
I just had my finger sharpened.

08:00.914 --> 08:04.149
If you don't throw
this surgery...You're dead.

08:04.151 --> 08:07.719
Owen, if you don't
ace this surgery, you're dead,

08:07.721 --> 08:10.322
