08:31.043 --> 08:34.111
Chief: <i> If you don't take a dive,</i>
<i>you're dead.</i>

08:34.114 --> 08:37.215
Sy:
<i>If you don't ace this surgery,</i>
<i>you're out on your ass.</i>

08:37.217 --> 08:40.585
Chief:
<i>I just had my finger sharpened.</i>

08:40.587 --> 08:43.587
Okay.
Pacemaker is in place.

08:43.590 --> 08:47.125
All we have to do now
is turn it on.

08:51.564 --> 08:53.965
Turn it on.

09:04.076 --> 09:05.443
[ power whirs down ]

09:05.445 --> 09:06.711
Male nurse: What's going on?

09:06.713 --> 09:07.612
