You're in on this, too?

09:25.631 --> 09:26.965
Finger him.

09:30.369 --> 09:32.003
Sorry, owen.

09:32.005 --> 09:33.305
[ metallic clang ]
[ groans ]

09:37.109 --> 09:38.577
