09:40.613 --> 09:42.347
Plaque!

09:43.583 --> 09:49.854
Let's finish this, dori.
[ monitors beeping steadily ]

09:49.856 --> 09:54.159
The nightmare's finally over --
for both of us.

09:54.161 --> 09:56.161
Weird that you shared
a jail cell

09:56.163 --> 09:59.497
With the ringleader of the crime
you were busted for.

09:59.499 --> 10:02.233
Sorry to put you through
all of that,

10:02.235 --> 10:02.901
