10:15.148 --> 10:17.415
Now that we know
this isn't your baby,

10:17.417 --> 10:18.917
I mean, what do we do?

10:18.919 --> 10:22.053
I would say for the next...
13 weeks,

10:22.055 --> 10:24.255
Let's just try
not to think about it.

10:24.257 --> 10:25.690
Sal: <i> Attention, staff.</i>

10:25.692 --> 10:27.092
<i>Will all available doctors</i>

10:27.094 --> 10:28.760
<i>Please report</i>
