10:29.830 --> 10:31.830
That is all.
Well, that's us.

10:31.832 --> 10:34.032
Let's get to work, huh?
Yep.

10:34.034 --> 10:35.634
Ah, it's so good
to be back

10:35.636 --> 10:37.535
In the old United States
of america.

10:37.537 --> 10:38.870
Yeah, we're in brazil.

10:38.872 --> 10:40.739
